INSERT INTO checklistItemResults (taskChecklistId, templateItemId, result, photoUrls)
SELECT 
  tc.id as taskChecklistId,
  cti.id as templateItemId,
  'na' as result,
  NULL as photoUrls
FROM taskChecklists tc
JOIN checklistTemplateItems cti ON cti.templateId = tc.templateId
LEFT JOIN checklistItemResults cir ON cir.taskChecklistId = tc.id AND cir.templateItemId = cti.id
WHERE cir.id IS NULL
ORDER BY tc.id, cti.order;
